%xhBackground Skills%xn represent arts, hobbies, professions and any other skills not covered by Action Skills.  Background Skills have a descriptive rating.   See [FS3: Background Skills](http://aresmush.com/fs3/fs3-3/chargen/#background-skills) for details.

Background Skills are free-form, so there is no specific list. You can pick anything from Singing to Underwater Basketweaving. Here are some ideas for Background Skills:

%xhA humanity%xn - history, literature, philosophy, poetry, etc.
%xhA profession or trade%xn - cook, barmaid, carpenter, brewer, blacksmith, brewer, seamstress, etc.
%xhA game%xn - chess, dice, checkers, cards, etc.
%xhAn art%xn - sculpting, painting, sketching, etc.
%xhA form of expression%xn - singing, dancing, playing an instrument, storytelling, etc.
%xhA craft or hobby%xn - gardening, basketweaving, knitting, etc.
%xhA religion%xn - Catholicism, Protestantism, Voodoo, Carib.

